<html>

<head>
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<style>
  .GFG {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    line-height: 2;
    display: inline-block;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background-image: linear-gradient(to top,#0084ff,#25b7ff);
    background-color: #0084ff;
    padding: 3px 20px;
    margin: 0;
    border: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>

<body>
  <h4>Dear {{name}},</h4>
  <p>
    You are receiving this email because you (or someone else) have requested the reset of the password for your
    account.
  </p>
  <p>
    Please click on the reset password button to complete the process within 2 hours of receiving it.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you did not request this, please ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.
  </p>
  <p>
    {{!-- <a href="{{passwordResetAddress}}">{{passwordResetAddress}}</a> --}}
    <a class="GFG" href = '{{passwordResetAddress}}'>
      Reset Password
    </a>
  </p>
</body>

</html>